metadata.name: Complicit #28 - Self Portrait with Elmar
metadata.description: Complicit, photographs of older men, is about the existential reality all humans face. The work has been the recipient of fellowships and grants from the New York Foundation for the Arts, New York University, and Columbia University, and has been featured in magazines across the world, such as The New Yorker, Vice Magazine, Dazed Magazine, and Artnet.
